cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.ET

The paper discusses security challenges and solutions in IoT networks, which are related to cryptography (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), software engineering (cs.SE), and embedded systems (cs.ET). However, since the focus is on hardware-based security mechanisms, cs.CR and cs.ET are the most likely categories.
